captions.text:
Today as soon as I got to the event I really
felt ready for this

competition, I knew it is going to be a good
day.

This year it's not just going to be a race
between me and

Orlando. I know Artem has now got new dives
and he is

really willing and really gunning for the
championship as well.
I know I have got to keep it going but anything
can happen in the next four events but it is definitely

a good feeling to
have a good start to the season.

For the competition in Norway I'm feeling
confident with my

dives now and for sure the other divers are
going to have to be
good and on form to beat me.

title: Red Bull Cliff Diving World Series 2010 - Mexico highlights
